            <p>
                jPBC is a Java docking framework to be used in cross-platform Swing applications.
                jPBC is an IntelliJ Idea like docking framework for managing secondary windows within the main
                window.
                jPBC allows to move,resize or extract those secondary windows.
                Also, jPBC provides support for content management of the main window.
                Like Eclipse, jPBC supports the concept of "prospective" using jPBC groups.
                <br/>
                <br/>
                <br/>
                <br/>
            </p>

